<topic template="Default" modified="2026-04-07T15:52:57.232Z" lasteditedby="noorhbo" version="2" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="../helpproject.xsd">
  <title>3.2 Low Oil Level Alarm in the Power Pack</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading3">动力组件中的低油位警报</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal">当动力组出现低油位警报时，请采取以下纠正措施：</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <list id="0" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:9px; font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:9px;">检查整个软管线路和接头是否有任何泄漏。如果发现泄漏，应立即处理。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:9px;">为动力组件重新注油。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal">检查 A 轴旋转接头处是否漏油。如有必要，更换旋转接头子单元。</li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">如需进一步帮助，请联系牧野服务代表。</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:9px; margin-left:13px; page-break-before:always;"></para>
  </body>
</topic>
